Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Challengers, adventurers, pioneers:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those who answer to that\Nkind of name are all fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart ones follow those fools,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they praise those who\Nsucceed and laugh at those who fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a star will never \Nstop challenging herself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and trying to be a real star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she is laughed at,\Nshe never stops running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fool aims high,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aspiring to be a real Kaleido Star, the\Nlikes of which have never been seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not acknowledge\Nthat you're a Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing New Rival."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is just so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those mysterious eyes are just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Sora will be in the show. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be in the show a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she here yet, Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, she's not in the\Ndressing room or the lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is such a bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah, you look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sixth sense tells me\Nthat she's in an absurd place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you look so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must think she's such a big\Nshot to be late on a day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marion, didn't you come\Nhere to help your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to see Leon Oswald!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince of the circus world from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pegasus of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the top talents in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his past is shrouded in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to talk\Nabout something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the first day that she's\Ngoing to perform with Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She still lacks a sense of being a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Miss Layla is gone,\Nwe lost some of our audience, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Sora worries about it in her\Nown way, so she's advertising the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my advertising helped a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, please come \Nvisit Kaleido Stage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a very wonderful show\Nwhich combines a play and acrobatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Layla's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, do that thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I have to get going soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! I'll do it just one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll take a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come visit Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come visit Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The worldwide top star, Mr. Leon Oswald,\Nwill appear on stage starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this "Saiyuki" is a love story,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't start without Sora,\Nwho plays the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, for the time \Nbeing, please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! We're opening the show, stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Mr. Leon came all the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be nice\Nif I advertised the show a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should think carefully\Nabout what you're supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's why I thought\NI should advertise and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a fur seal can do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand what Boss wants to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still can't draw in the audience\Ndoing just my show like Miss Layla, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, Mr. Leon. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's time to perform\Nin front of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I look forward to performing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to appear on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle the stage myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to be saying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on stage, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he was serious\Nabout doing it all himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go change clothes quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to take it off, I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only want you to\Ntake off the animal costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said "damn," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "damn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now stay still. You don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You did say it! You did, you did, you {\i1}did{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd go to heaven or something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after we perfected the \Nlegendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a spirit, not... a... ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made Mr. Leon mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll forgive me if I work really\Nhard and make the show exciting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your constellation is Sagittarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the sign for heading\Nstraight for your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have enough radiance yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road to true stardom is still a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my dream, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be Miss Layla's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can become a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's all right. Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--which means that you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to do my best however I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all! That's all! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. They like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like my first\Nstrategy worked just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go to the second strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, with this Mr. Leon will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it. He's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go back to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of plans. We're going to\Nput on the clown show right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in the middle of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have to show them a\Nhalf-done job, it's better not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not nice to the audience\Nwho took the time to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience came here to see me at my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A show in which I don't shine is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't we go out on stage\Nto make the audience happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think the show must go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here for the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience is here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the greatest\Ntechnical skill in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience needs only\Ncome to the theater to admire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew Kaleido Stage was a place\Nthat puts on stupid performances
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to pander to the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have come here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are children who don't\Nknow anything about your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids are not my audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew the one who perfected\Nthat legendary great maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was this kind of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do have the best\Ntechnical skills in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the current Kaleido Stage needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my skills alone can't draw\Nin the audience like in old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't leave, Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clown show is about to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way! What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't cancel the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Leon won't be in the show,\NI will finish it by myself if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I manage to finish the show all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you remain at Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not make any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do it, go \Nahead, do as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn that the\Naudience is a performer's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the audience have to be our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing both roles means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to do your maneuvers as well\Nas Mr. Leon's continually without a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physically, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what are you going to do with the last\Nscene where the two of them meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ken. I have to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to pull this off no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good! I can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla entrusted Kaleido Stage to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens, I have to protect it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to protect Kaleido Stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we need Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what kind of person he is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids are not my audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those children are also an\Nimportant part of the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like when I was a child and\NI saw the show for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was whimsical and it was fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot myself in watching the show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is the Kaleido Stage. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N- -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a quick change...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not allowed to show a tired look.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sora must have reached her limit,\Nsince she's been going nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a person as reckless as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone who\Ngoes as far as she does, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who becomes a real\Nshining star could be someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying monsters while spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing on top of that mountain\Nwhile spinning is difficult in and of itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since she is staggering that much,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she has no choice but to slow down the spin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if she does that, the\Nmaneuver will be incomplete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's speeding up? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's so awkward. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't keep watching her. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without a doubt,\NI've never seen her type before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora Naegino... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last scene is the \Nreunion with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point, the directing will\Nchange depending on Sora's ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I will give you instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, turn off the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-5, turn the spot light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, she is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the light off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the B light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I pulled it off! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the last scenes, I should throw\Nmyself into the protagonist's state of mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And hold her gently with all my love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a hike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon! Leon! Leon! Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon! Leon! Leon! Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon! Leon! Leon! Leon! Leon! Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn that the\Naudience is a performer's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her performance went well, but they...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful, Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were rejected as Leon\NOswald's partner, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're performing for two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Let them continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she a trapeze artist? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal Angel Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She uses the swing so easily and freely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's so bold, and her performance\Nis overflowing with confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be Leon's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you cannot, Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she's the girl who passed with\Nthe highest scores in this year's audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this part of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's pretty cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is totally my kind of gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the next Layla Hamilton!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will be the Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I won't let you call yourself\Na Kaleido Star when you have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If either of them could be my partner,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it might be worth it to \Nstay on a little longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind staying here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll appear on stage with me--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with you. With me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon certainly is great.\NHe can see how talented I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you. Ad-lib and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the girl who passed\Naudition with the top score.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May Wong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to protect the Kaleido Stage\Nthat Miss Layla entrusted to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one fit to be a Kaleido Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not you! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new Kaleido Stage has been set in motion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, \NI've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell \Nphone and charge my love{\i0}
